Class AstroCoordSystem

java.lang.Object

All Implemented Interfaces:
org.ivoa.vodml.jaxb.XmlIdManagement, org.ivoa.vodml.jpa.JPAManipulations, org.ivoa.vodml.jpa.JPAManipulationsForObjectType<Long>
@Entity @VoDml(id="coords:AstroCoordSystem", role=objectType) public class AstroCoordSystem extends CoordSys implements org.ivoa.vodml.jpa.JPAManipulationsForObjectType<Long>, org.ivoa.vodml.jaxb.XmlIdManagement
The AstroCoordSystem object holds a collection of component coordinate system descriptions across all represented physical domains. objectType: AstroCoordSystem
